name: BARFI
description:
Hey,
My name is Barfi and I am a stray cat living in the street, A beautiful soul having an eye on me and each time I visit her balcony she leaves food for me carefully so she doesn't scare me away, By purchasing my NFT you will help to support me and my pals who also lives in the street.

We love and support stray animals. The sales profit of this collection will be used to support a few individual shelter who does rescue animals. To see the cats story visit @6lovely.cats on Instagram.

Illustrations by @manisaemi
